\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.869223402540908*^9, 
  3.86922349632195*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"804dce74-f0ba-4df3-999b-\
230b87bda602"],

Cell["\<\
IPOtoDeSPACReturn:\t\tOne-year post-merger return measured from the IPO of \
the SPAC\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.869223402540908*^9, 
  3.869223531165839*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d9a76166-6b9e-48ef-8674-\
999ecfe0ed5a"],

Cell["\<\
IPOtoDeSPACAR:\t\tOn-year post-merger AR measured from the IPO of the SPAC\
